headline: NWSA Q4 Deep Dive: Digital Growth, AI Content Licensing, and Real Estate Momentum
summary: Global media and publishing company News Corp (NASDAQ:NWSA) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 5.5% year on year to $2.36 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.40 per share was 6.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
